{"word":"καταβολή","slug":"καταβολή","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b><el>ϰαταβολή, ῆς, ἡ</el></b> [<el><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:καταβάλλω\">καταβάλλω</a></el>] <b>foundation, establishment,</b> <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ w.\">w.</a> <el><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:κόσμος\">κόσμος</a></el> (<b><a href='B:470 13:35'>Mt 13:35</a></b> <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ al.\">al.</a>) except <b><a href='B:650 11:11'>Hb 11:11</a>,</b> where the imagery of sowing seed relates to conception. <center id=\"nav_bottom\"> <a id=\"left_arrow\" href=\"S:καταβοάω\">&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;</a> <a id=\"bottom_home\" href=\"S:#1.Table of Contents\">&emsp;&emsp;</a> <a id=\"right_arrow\" href=\"S:καταβραβεύω\">&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;</a> </center> "}]}